Impact Players(Justin Credible and Lance Storm (3))

column8: At CyberSlam, Justin Credible threw down the titles to become eligible for the ECW World Heavyweight Championship. Storm later left for World Championship Wrestling. As a result of the circumstances, Credible vacated the championship.
